    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;Since file-upload is a feature that will benefit many applications, this proposes an extension to HTML to allow information providers to express file upload requests uniformly, and a MIME compatible representation for file upload responses.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
